sequenceDiagram
	participant browser
	participant server

	browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa
	activate server
	server-->>browser: HTML document
	deactivate server

	Note right of browser: The HTML document contains no POST requests, just HTML and the javascript embed

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/main.css
    activate server
    server-->>browser: The css file
    deactivate server

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/spa.js
    activate server
    server-->>browser: The Javascript file, but it's the single-page app version
    deactivate server

	Note right of browser: The Javascript for the SPA handles the requests for data as well as the DOM modification

    browser->>server: GET https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/data.json
    activate server
    server-->>browser: [{"content": "test spa","date": "2025-12-08T09:21:16.682Z"},...]
    deactivate server

	Note right of server: After sending spa.js and the main HTML, the server only sends data, no rendered HTML

	
